playerName=glenn+sherlock&playerStats=index.html&previous=speier&next=murphy&playerBio=bullpen coach
born: Sept. 26, 1960; Nahant, Mass.
lives: Scottsdale
former position: catcher

Now in his fourth season as the D-Backs' bullpen/catching coach, his 21st overall year in pro ball. Sherlock keeps track of opposing team's lineup card allowing relivers to be prepared of the situation when they enter the game. Spent 10 seasons in the Yankees organization as a minor league player, coach and manager.
